  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Implement in React Native (Expo). Do not use HTML/CSS DOM elements like div, span.",
    "Ensure all interactive components use data-testid (or testID acting as data-testid) for automated testing.",
    "Use deep/dark themes prominently as per palette. Avoid solid white backgrounds.",
    "Leverage React Native Reanimated or standard Animated API for subtle avatar floats (breathing effect).",
    "For the bottom nav bar, utilize a BlurView or similar native component to achieve the frosted glass effect."
  ]
